{"tid":2297113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB電視城染疫　30人要做檢測","createTime":"2020-11-23T05:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T05:31:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adde39ee464c98e85897d09cc85367cabc096281","tid":2297113,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情肆虐，無綫電視今日（23日）向員工發通告，一名在電視廣播城工作的會計女文員昨日(22日)通知公司確診新冠肺炎，已在醫院進行隔離。她最後上班日期為上周五（20日），無綫電視指已在會計科進行消毒清潔，另有約30名與她有接觸的同事前往接受檢測，至今約10人收到檢測結果，均無確診。<br />\n<br />\n無綫電視表示，政府已呼籲市民盡量減少外出用膳，並避免不必要的社交活動包括私人聚會，建議同事要時刻注意個人及環境衞生，經常佩戴口罩及保持雙手清潔。當出現呼吸道感染病徵，不應上班及盡早求診。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on. cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201123/bkn-20201123122220357-1123_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"473de5fec2d77b8de0b8bdb4659f0c8630a2a7cf","tid":2297113,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03544c21d672b1f30802e32b0696d7de5cdd6b2","tid":2297113,"uid":35623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"期待台慶群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89e556793e0d160ba7489a04e38be42e64afc46","tid":2297113,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"係咪new god 美斯/帶棗兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5fd6f8112fd8ca1388662038ace1821ccd383a","tid":2297113,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9703537c232fc7df6a412ae112d1e2d7cab02a","tid":2297113,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"生化電視城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e536008c2ad2b6f4f9da10e15cbb821275be12e2","tid":2297113,"uid":177485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"萬千星輝賀感染"},{"pid":"9e8a942a149a46e6ae4dfd6cd7e3c68aa7a3a070","tid":2297113,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNvsLLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNvsLLh.png&h=89ed8c0e&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\"><strong>《無綫就嚟執笠? TVB戰線，你唔知道嘅5件事!》</strong></p></span></strong></span><br />\n1️⃣ 派嬲人數勁減一半。舊團隊被捕後，TVB戰線回復唔返原先狀態，較去年同期，而家派嬲嘅人起碼急降50%以上，長期不足1000人，PR公司未必夠理據說服品牌轉用其他宣傳渠道。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 新廣告仍然源源不絕，有大公司，有小店，台慶前一晚我先入咗30個廣告商落excel表。<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ BigBigShop加盟店源源不絕。我哋一直都強調BBS嘅潛在威脅性，因為HKTV就係靠網購起死回生，近期BBS商品已經突破五萬件，但抵制BBS任務仍然未受大家重視，所以希望大家唔好揀任嚟做。<br />\n<br />\n4️⃣ 有廣告業朋友透露，如果喺其他渠道賣廣告嘅效果不如TVB，即使會俾網民鬧，品牌都會硬著頭皮返返TVB賣廣告，換言之，佢哋覺得賣廣告帶嚟嘅營業額&gt;被抵制而減少嘅營業額，所以大家真係要派多啲嬲，令更多人知道邊啲品牌係TVB廣告商，抵制先有更大成效。<br />\n<br />\n5️⃣ 前排笑完TVB (0511)股價就嚟穿6，但而家已經上返7蚊。<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post唔係想放負，一場抗爭，出捷報維持士氣係重要，但唔能夠一味靠自high維持，大家見到多正牆紙割蓆好開心，但其實TVB戰線近呢半年嚟都非常嚴峻，如果大家唔正視，又缺乏新血加入，呢條線好難靠幾百人守得住，時刻警戒，驕兵必敗。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係第一次睇我哋嘅文，又或者唔係經常參與我哋活動嘅手足，希望你由今日開始，加入我哋，多謝🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">【TVB戰線懶人區】(最後更新22 Nov 2110)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">【紅媒金主】HOME+、鴻福堂 (21 Nov)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/104593468121466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F104593468121466&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=0716d661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/104593468121466</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/78764398214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F78764398214&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=b03aed23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/78764398214</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2295084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2295084</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">【紅媒金主】HKBN (20 Nov)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/203223348795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F203223348795&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=7289a77e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/203223348795</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2293776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2293776</a><br />\n<br />\n《萬千嬲嬲賀台慶》 (19 Nov)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2292377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2292377</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">【紅媒金主】尖沙咀食肆 (17 Nov)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/1531723607053926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F1531723607053926&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=23a2cf0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/1531723607053926</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/474502252887910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F474502252887910&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=4d7cadaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/474502252887910</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/257293771781659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F257293771781659&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=ac37449f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/257293771781659</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2289774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2289774</a><br />\n<br />\n【紅媒金主】合興 獅球嘜 (15 Nov)<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/180410908649803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F180410908649803&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=a900be89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/180410908649803</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2287077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2287077</a></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCredits to 抵制Cctvb 團隊"}]}